{"tid":1807203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔跪警察都係垃圾","createTime":"2020-01-01T16:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T16:52:14.000Z","uid":12269,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"199ec94b4b472b51118a5c3763bb9271a063c666","tid":1807203,"uid":12269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:38:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">垃圾幾時先明白 呢個世界冇唔尊重警察呢回事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">1.唔跪對狗隻零傷害 係零傷害 佢地照準時出糧拎OT 佢地一條毛都冇少</span><br />\n所以大家為手足安全，跪一跪警察，等佢地個心好過啲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">2.唔跪會增加自己或手足被捕風險</span><br />\n所以大家為手足安全，跪一跪警察，等佢地個心好過啲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">3.實際成效?</span><br />\n唔跪有咩成效<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">4.沒有唔跪 只有打狗</span><br />\n你需要做既係隨時有心理準備打狗/救人/著草 係 呢樣先係你應該要做既野 唔係唔進行跪拜<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n總結:唔好再on99以為自己係主人，你先係狗</span>"},{"pid":"b3ea4b8daf26dc108a2f4915e2a0c7f4e88c7e7d","tid":1807203,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:38:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">［急尋人！］</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1月1日 銅鑼灣citibank前被捕手足去向 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1807139\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1807139</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求幫推"},{"pid":"c6452927390b57b0a6d72db3e92b6074beb528a6","tid":1807203,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:40:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\